{"file_name": "Advocate_multipage.pdf", "file_type": "pdf", "confidence": 0.77, "time_taken": 0.55, "memory_mb": 3.31, "units": [{"index": 1, "method": "structured", "confidence": 0.77, "text": {"text": "ADV. RAHUL SHARMA\nSenior Advocate / Legal Consultant\nNew Delhi, India | rahul.sharma@email.com | +91-9XXXXXXXXX\nPROFESSIONAL SUMMARY\nAdvocate with 11+ years of experience in civil, criminal, and commercial litigation. Extensive practice before\nDistrict Courts, High Courts, and Tribunals. Known for strong legal drafting, courtroom advocacy, and client\nadvisory skills across diverse legal matters.\nAREAS OF PRACTICE\n(cid:127) Civil & Commercial Litigation\n(cid:127) Criminal Law & Procedure\n(cid:127) Corporate & Contract Law\n(cid:127) Arbitration & Dispute Resolution\n(cid:127) Legal Drafting & Opinions\nPROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE\nSenior Advocate \u2013 Sharma & Associates (2017 \u2013 Present)\n(cid:127) Represent clients in complex litigation matters before District Courts and High Courts.\n(cid:127) Draft pleadings, agreements, contracts, and legal opinions for corporate and individual clients.\n(cid:127) Successfully argued over 120 matters with a success rate exceeding 75%.\n(cid:127) Advised companies on regulatory compliance and dispute resolution.", "tables": []}}, {"index": 2, "method": "structured", "confidence": 0.76, "text": {"text": "Legal Associate \u2013 Verma Legal Chambers (2012 \u2013 2017)\n(cid:127) Assisted senior counsels in litigation strategy, drafting, and research.\n(cid:127) Appeared independently for procedural hearings and tribunal matters.\n(cid:127) Conducted legal research and prepared case briefs for senior advocates.\n(cid:127) Managed client communication and case documentation.\nKEY ACHIEVEMENTS\n(cid:127) Successfully handled high-value commercial disputes exceeding INR 50 Crores.\n(cid:127) Recognized for precision in legal drafting and argumentation.\nEDUCATION\n(cid:127) Bachelor of Laws (LL.B) \u2013 University of Delhi\